(async (manager) => {\n   225\t     await manager.save(match);\n   226\t     thi
s.server.to(roomId).emit("match:created", payload); // 数据可能还未写入\n   227\
t   });\n   228\t   ```\n   229\t\n   230\t4. **Payload 类型**：必须使用 `shared
-types` 中定义的 DTO/Interface，禁止内联 `any`\n   231\t\n   232\t   ```typescri
pt\n   233\t   // ✅ 正确\n   234\t   import { MatchCreatedEvent } from "@social
